          <p style="color: #232368;font-size:14px;text-align:center">Short sell your coins to maximize your returns in a bear market. When you hit a price floor, you can buy them back and pocket big earnings on your way back up.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <div class="service-item">
