        </p>
        <div class="service-detail">
          <h4 style="text-align:center; color: #232368;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold !important;">Trailing Stop-Loss</h4>
          <p style="color: #232368;font-size:14px;text-align:center">Just like a rock climber belaying up a cliff, trailing stop-loss tracks your coin up and only sells when it hits a drop. This allows you to climb the upwards trend, and never sell too early!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
